completeDescription: This beautiful house is perfect for a family looking for a spacious, comfortable home in a peaceful and safe neighborhood. Featuring three bedrooms and two bathrooms, this single-family home boasts a generous 2,000 square feet of living space, with an additional 500 square feet of space in the finished basement.
